Uses of Class
cutter.math.CalculationMethod

  • Packages that use CalculationMethod 
    Package Description
    cutter.math.vectors
    The cutter.math.vectors package contains all classes for vector-calculations (3D only)

    • Uses of CalculationMethod in cutter.math.vectors

      Constructors in cutter.math.vectors with parameters of type CalculationMethod 
      Constructor and Description
      Point3D(double x, double y, double z, CalculationMethod calculationMethod)
      Defines a Point and adds the declaration as MathML in the CalculationMethod object
      Vector3D(double xComponent, double yComponent, double zComponent, CalculationMethod calculationMethod)
      This creates a Vector3D by its components and saves every calculation step as MathML in the CalculationMethod pbject
      Vector3D(Point3D startingPoint, Point3D endPoint, CalculationMethod calculationMethod)
      Creates a Vector between the given points and saves every calculation step as MathML in the CalculationMethod object
